	<p>This innovative staircase, designed by the president of Berg Furniture, offers a creative new twist on the traditional ladder. The non-slip treads, wide and roomy steps, and comfortable handrail provide safe and easy access to the top loft. New from Berg and included in every staircase: an LED light to illuminate the stairs at night triggered by motion! Each step is equipped with an extra deep drawer to maximize storage capacity. The stairs are sturdy enough for parents to use too! Stairs are can be installed on either the left or right side of the system.</p>
